snippet.title: Dash-Da-Dash DX 17,777,900 EX Mode
snippet.description:
A fun, free and addictive game you can find here:
http://renard.teknolust.org/ddd/

Currently, this is the best score posted on the leader boards by a sizable margin. I took a lot of chances and survived a number of close calls. Accidentally clicking outside the window and pausing the game gets annoying. This happens towards the end.

Good luck beating this one!
